Right to Request Deletion
You may submit your request to delete your Personal Data by visiting: "My-Setting-Account and Security-Delete Account". Whenyou confirm the deletion of your account, your Personal Data will be deleted accordingly.
Right to Opt-out of the Sale of Personal Data
The CCPA allows you to opt-out the sale of your Personal Data. To opt-out of these “sales”, please follow the
